'''2015年2月福特寇恐怖襲擊'''，是指2015年2月4日一宗發生在[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]]城市{{link-en|福特寇|Fotokol}}、由[[博科聖地|博科聖地]]發動的[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]襲擊，造成大量死傷。

== 過程 ==
在襲擊發生前數小時，喀麥隆鄰國[[乍得|乍得]]派兵打擊博科聖地，在[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]{{link-en|嘉波魯|Gamboru}}殺死了超過200名博科聖地武裝份子；有些武裝份子逃離嘉波魯，來到距離當地{{convert|500|yd}}的福特寇<ref name=war>{{cite news |author1=Thomas Barrabi |title=Boko Haram Massacres Civilians, Burns Down Mosque In Cameroon Days Before Nigeria Presidential Election |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/boko-haram-massacres-civilians-burns-down-mosque-cameroon-days-nigeria-presidential-1805036 |accessdate=2015-09-19 |agency=International Business Times |date=2015-02-04 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150919023633/http://www.ibtimes.com/boko-haram-massacres-civilians-burns-down-mosque-cameroon-days-nigeria-presidential-1805036 |archivedate=2015-09-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2015年2月4日，他們在福特寇的[[民居|民居]]和[[清真寺|清真寺]]殺害平民，並在不少[[建築物|建築物]]上[[縱火|縱火]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Boko Haram 'kill 70' in Cameroon border town of Fotokol |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-31141097 |accessdate=2015-09-18 |agency=BBC |date=2015-02-04 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150205011826/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-31141097 |archivedate=2015-02-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，有受害者的喉嚨遭到割開<ref>{{cite news |title=Boko Haram kills dozens in rampage after Chad offensive |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-2939154/Cameroon-troops-clash-Boko-Haram-border-town.html |accessdate=2015-09-18 |date=2015-02-05 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150918163545/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-2939154/Cameroon-troops-clash-Boko-Haram-border-town.html |archivedate=2015-09-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。有些武裝份子挨家挨戶地上門殺人，也有武裝份子在街上射殺民眾；他們縱火焚燒最少三所清真寺，屠殺其中一所清真寺包括[[伊瑪目|伊瑪目]]在內的善信<ref>{{cite news |author1=Aminu Abubakar |title=Boko Haram massacres scores in Cameroon town, residents say |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/02/04/world/boko-haram-attack/ |accessdate=2015-09-18 |agency=CNN |date=2015-02-05 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150918172305/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/02/04/world/boko-haram-attack/ |archivedate=2015-09-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。有平民被博科聖地武裝份子用作[[人肉盾牌|人肉盾牌]]<ref name=USA/>。

由於查證資料方面出現困難，不同資料來源提供的數據互相矛盾，此次襲擊的死難者數量也未有定論<ref>{{cite news |author1=Yerima Kini Nsom |title=How Boko Haram Littered Fotokol Mosques With Corpses |url=http://www.cameroonpostline.com/how-boko-haram-littered-fotokol-mosques-with-corpses/ |accessdate=2015-09-19 |agency=Cameroon Postline |date=2015-02-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150919020403/http://www.cameroonpostline.com/how-boko-haram-littered-fotokol-mosques-with-corpses/ |archivedate=2015-09-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。福特寇有消息來源向[[法新社|法新社]]表示，是次恐怖襲擊造成接近76人死亡，其中6人是軍人，其餘均為平民；當地亦有民间领袖與[[路透社|路透社]]記者通電話，表示武裝份子共殺害了超過100人<ref>{{cite news |title=Boko Haram massacre reported in Cameroon town |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/02/dozens-reported-killed-boko-haram-raid-cameroon-150204204704396.html |accessdate=2015-09-18 |agency=Al Jazeera |date=2015-02-05 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150918161722/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/02/dozens-reported-killed-boko-haram-raid-cameroon-150204204704396.html |archivedate=2015-09-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。襲擊也造成近500人受傷<ref name=USA>{{cite news |title=Boko Haram fighters attack town in Niger |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/boko-haram-fighters-attack-town-in-niger-1.2947445 |accessdate=2015-09-19 |agency=The Associated Press |date=2015-02-06 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150919042901/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/boko-haram-fighters-attack-town-in-niger-1.2947445 |archivedate=2015-09-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

襲擊發生後，乍得的部隊對博科聖地展開攻擊，冀能打擊進行是次襲擊的武裝份子<ref name=war/>。

== 反應 ==
[[聯合國安全理事會|聯合國安全理事會]]譴責包括這宗襲擊在內的一些博科聖地恐怖活動<ref>{{cite news |title=Security Council condemns Boko Haram attacks along Chad-Cameroon border |url=http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=50012 |accessdate=2015-09-19 |agency=United Nations News Centre |date=2015-02-05 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150919072343/http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=50012%23.Vf0NduLLfK4 |archivedate=2015-09-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]以「最强烈而又可行的措辞」，譴責這宗襲擊和博科聖地在[[尼日爾|尼日爾]]發動的另一宗襲擊，又批評博科聖地是無限地殘暴和野蠻<ref name=USA />。[[阿爾及利亞|阿爾及利亞]]對博科聖地在福特寇、{{link-en|博索|Bosso, Niger}}和{{link-en|迪法|Diffa}}發動的恐怖襲擊作出大力譴責，又表示與[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]、喀麥隆、尼日爾及乍得的「兄弟人民」和政府團結一致<ref>{{cite news |title=Algeria vigorously condemns Boko Haram’s terrorist attacks in Cameroon, Niger |url=http://www.aps.dz/en/algeria/6000-algeria-vigourously-condemns-boko-haram%E2%80%99s-terrorist-attacks-in-cameroun,-niger |accessdate=2015-09-19 |agency=ALGERIA PRESS SERVICE |date=2015-02-07 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150919052025/http://www.aps.dz/en/algeria/6000-algeria-vigourously-condemns-boko-haram%E2%80%99s-terrorist-attacks-in-cameroun,-niger |archivedate=2015-09-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

